fields.title: User Policies for Test and Exams.
fields.content:
USER POLICIES FOR TEST AND EXAMS

  1. SAMPLE TEST:
      Open direct brainbooks.pk page (without longin) and generate SAMPLE TEST.

  2. FOR PAID REGISTRATION FEE FOR SCHOOL/ACADEMY WITH NAME AND LOGO: FOR 12 MONTHS
    • For Matric OR Inter classes Annual Unlimited Package: Rs.7,000/- separately.
    • For Matric AND Inter classes Annual Unlimited Package: Rs.13,000/-.

  3. HOW TO DEPOSIT FEE:
    OPTION-1:
    JazzCash Business:
    Follow the instructions:
    Dial *786*10# and write Till ID 00130481
    OR scan QR Code than WhatsApp Institution Name,
    Logo, Address, Cell # alongwith Fee Transaction
    detail on:0322-4223373
    OR
    Easypaisa Account
    Syed Ali-ul-Husnain
    03224223373

    OPTION-2:
    Bank Account:
    HBL: BRAIN BOOKS,
    Urdu Bazar, Lahore
    Account # 01367900270903

  4. FOR FREE REGISTRATION FEE FOR SCHOOL/ACADEMY WITH NAME AND LOGO:
    • For one year Free Registration with SCHOOL NAME and LOGO, buy 25 sets of BRAIN QUESTION BANK for Class 9th & 10th each at least.

  5. HOW TO REGISTER LOGIN AND PASSWORD:
    • Signup your account profile with your name, email, password, cell number and save your profile / information.
    • Now login with your email and password and open My Account page (from top right corner).
    • Fill up your school name and address and share your Brain ID (second from top) and LOGO with admin on WhatsApp # 03334223373.
    • Contact ADMIN for authorization.

  6. FEATURES FOR PAID USERS:
    • Generate unlimited Tests / Papers of any subject of different marks.
    • Generate single, multiple or full book test / papers.
    • Generate Short Test, Full Test, MCQs Test or SQs+LQs Test separately.
    • Registration period will be for ONE YEAR (12 months).

  7. FEATURES FOR FREE USERS:
    • For Free Users no need to signup website just open directly.
    • Enjoy unlimited Free Online Chapter-wise MCQs Test.
    • Get Print of All Boards’ Past Papers.
    • The Questions DATABASE is updated on regular basis.
    • Study our other products (books, up-to-dates) etc.
    • Get paper pairing scheme / scheme of studies of all subjects.
    • Get any boards’ result through link given in menu bar.

  8. PRINT SETTING:
    • Before Generating a TEST press Ctrl+F5 key to refresh / load Question DATABASE.
    • After Generating Test/Paper Click PRINT icon (in blue bar top left).
    • In print menu always open MORE SETTING (left below).
    • Set paper size A4 or Legal as per your requirement.
    • In margins use custom option.
    • Click in print preview page.
    • Drag dot lines left and right to set print page.
    • In general keep scale 100.

  9. FOR COMMENTS USE:
    • Online Feedback Comments.
    • Email : info@brainbooks.pk; brainbooks66@gmail.com
    • WhatsApp No.0322-0333/4223373
    • Facebook Page: BrainBooksLahore
    • SMS : 0322-0333/4223373
    • Landline :042-37113344

fields.title: This is my about us page.
fields.content:
Testmaker is an online facility capable of facilitating its customers with the best services regarding education. It is mainly designed to help the teachers to prepare tests of different classes with a variety of options. Here even students can take advantage and make their own assessments after learning. We are living in the time where getting best grades is important for a glorious future. Grades can only be achieved by continuous learning and evaluation. For this purpose tests are very important as they play a significant role in identifying student’s problem areas where special attention is required and for that multiple tests are necessary.

Testmaker is the solution to all your paper generating problems. We are introducing two major level tests: Advanced and Exercise Based. In Advanced level tests all types of questions will be asked including conceptual ones while the exercise based tests will only be made from the exercise questions of the textbooks. Also the tests can be made from one or more chapters.

Our special feature is the manual selection of questions. You can select questions of your choice from our database. Where others only provide random automatically generated papers, we not only generate random papers but also give you access to make paper as you desire. The papers will consist of the number of section of your selection. Our database comprises of a vast range of subjective and objective questions necessarily required for a proper and appropriate evaluation of knowledge.

Currently we are working on many projects like online lectures, data of intermediate classes and many other private publications. These will be uploaded soon.
